	<div id="drc" class="tabs-content">

		<section><div class="title"><h2>Informationen</h2></div><table class="index-list tdvam"><colgroup><col style="width:20%"><col style="width:80%"></colgroup><tr class="odd"><td class="grey"><img src="http://cdn.anisearch.com/media/country/ja.png" class="flag" alt="ja">Titel</td><td><span lang="ja">Seikai no Senki III</span> <i lang="ja" class="grey">星界の戦旗III</i></td></tr><tr><td class="grey"><img src="http://cdn.anisearch.com/media/country/xx.png" class="flag" alt="xx">Synonyme</td><td>Banner of the Stars 3, Banner of the Stars III, Seikai no Senki 3</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td class="grey">Typ / Anzahl</td><td>OVA, 2 <span class="grey">(&#126;<time datetime="PT0H37M">37min</time>)</span></td></tr><tr><td class="grey">Status</td><td><table><colgroup><col style="width:25%"><col style="width:32%"><col style="width:43%"></colgroup><tr><td><img src="http://cdn.anisearch.com/media/country/ja.png" class="flag" alt="ja"> Abgeschlossen</td><td class="f12g">06.08.2005</td><td><a href="company/318,sunrise" class="f12">Sunrise</a></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr class="odd"><td class="grey">Adaptiert von</td><td><a href="anime/index/?char=all&amp;sort=stars&amp;order=desc&amp;tag_include=98">Light Novel</a></td></tr><tr><td class="grey">Hauptgenre</td><td><ul class="cloud clearfix"><li><a rel="nofollow" href="anime/index/?char=all&amp;sort=stars&amp;order=desc&amp;genre_include=14" class="gg">Abenteuer</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class="odd"><td class="grey">Nebengenres</td><td><ul class="cloud clearfix"><li><a rel="nofollow" href="anime/index/?char=all&amp;sort=stars&amp;order=desc&amp;category_include=1" class="gc">Abenteuer</a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" href="anime/index/?char=all&amp;sort=stars&amp;order=desc&amp;category_include=2" class="gc">Action</a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" href="anime/index/?char=all&amp;sort=stars&amp;order=desc&amp;category_include=4" class="gc">Drama</a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" href="anime/index/?char=all&amp;sort=stars&amp;order=desc&amp;category_include=31" class="gc">Männlich</a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" href="anime/index/?char=all&amp;sort=stars&amp;order=desc&amp;category_include=21" class="gc">Romanze</a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" href="anime/index/?char=all&amp;sort=stars&amp;order=desc&amp;category_include=23" class="gc">Sci-Fi</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td class="grey">Tags</td><td><ul class="cloud clearfix"><li><a rel="nofollow" href="anime/index/?char=all&amp;sort=stars&amp;order=desc&amp;tag_include=103" class="gt">Krieg</a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" href="anime/index/?char=all&amp;sort=stars&amp;order=desc&amp;tag_include=104" class="gt">Militär</a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" href="anime/index/?char=all&amp;sort=stars&amp;order=desc&amp;tag_include=107" class="gt">Space Opera</a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" href="anime/index/?char=all&amp;sort=stars&amp;order=desc&amp;tag_include=36" class="gt">Weltraum</a></li></ul></td></tr></table></section><section><div class="title mtC"><h2>Beschreibung</h2></div> <span data-id="de" class="desc-xx sbutton bcolorC">Deutsch</span> <span data-id="en" class="desc-xx sbutton">Englisch</span><div itemprop="description" lang="de" id="desc-de" class="desc-zz textblock mtB">Nach dem erfolgreichen Abschluss der Operation "Hunter" wurden die verbliebenen Streitkräfte der Vereinigten Menschheit zerstört. <a href="character/889,jinto-linn">Jintos</a> Heimatwelt "Martine" geriet nach dem Rückzug der Vereinigten Menschheit wieder in den Einflussbereich des Abh-Imperiums. Jinto verließ daraufhin die Raumflotte, um als Graf die Verwaltung des Planeten zu übernehmen. <a href="character/117,lafiel">Lafiel</a> begleitet ihn auf seiner Reise.<br /><br />Basiert auf den Romanen von <a href="person/6719,hiroyuki-morioka">Hiroyuki Morioka</a>.</div><div itemprop="description" lang="en" id="desc-en" class="desc-zz textblock mtB hidden">Jinto and Lafiel were traveling on the light-armed transport ship Bokbrusue to the Hyde System (which returned to imperial rule after the Union retreated), in order for Jinto (now an earl) to take over the government. However, the government of Martin, Jinto's motherland, resisted obstinately against imperial rule. On the other side, the First Devastation Fleet—formed with a new ship type, the "Attack Vessel"—traveled to the Hyde System for drilling practice…<div class="mtC f10g">Source: <a href="http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/encyclopedia/anime.php?id=4899" class="f10g bold">ANN</a></div></div></section><section><div class="title mtC"><h2>Artikel</h2><div class="showall"><a href="anime/3527,seikai-no-senki-iii/articles">Alle anzeigen</a></div></div><div class="itembox"><a rel="nofollow" href="redirect/item/2944822759/7937" target="_blank"><img src="http://cdn.anisearch.com/images/article/cover/thumb/7/7937.jpg" height="120" alt="Seikai No Senki III - ED: &quot;Tenohira no Yume&quot;" title="&lt;img src=&quot;http://cdn.anisearch.com/images/article/cover/full/7/7937.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;f12&quot;&gt;Seikai No Senki III - ED: &quot;Tenohira no Yume&quot;&lt;br&gt;Release: 2005-11-04&lt;/div&gt;" class="article-spacer img fullsizeA"></a></div></section><section><script>var Screens=[780,42319,156250,777,42320,156244,42321,156242,156251];</script><a id="screenshots" data-id="3527" data-type="anime"> </a><div class="title mtC"><h2>Screenshots</h2><div class="showall"><span id="showall_screens" class="afake">Alle anzeigen</span></div></div><a itemprop="thumbnailUrl" href="http://cdn.anisearch.com/images/anime/screen/3/3527/full/42310.jpg" class="zoom"><img itemprop="image" src="http://cdn.anisearch.com/images/anime/screen/3/3527/thumb/42310.jpg" width="220" alt="Seikai no Senki III" class="screen"></a><a itemprop="thumbnailUrl" href="http://cdn.anisearch.com/images/anime/screen/3/3527/full/42315.jpg" class="zoom"><img itemprop="image" src="http://cdn.anisearch.com/images/anime/screen/3/3527/thumb/42315.jpg" width="220" alt="Seikai no Senki III" class="screen"></a><a itemprop="thumbnailUrl" href="http://